"```sql\nSELECT yearmonth.CustomerID, MIN(yearmonth.Consumption) AS LeastConsumption\nFROM yearmonth\nJOIN customers ON yearmonth.CustomerID = customers.CustomerID\nWHERE yearmonth.Date BETWEEN '201201' AND '201212' \nAND customers.Segment = 'LAM'\nGROUP BY yearmonth.CustomerID\nORDER BY LeastConsumption ASC\nLIMIT 1;\n```"